  afbinit-1.0.1-r2.ebuild:
  Mark 1.0.1-r1 stable for sparc, and add ~keyword to 1.0.1-r2 for testing:
  1.0.1-r2 is required for afb (Elite) systems which are running 2.6.x kernels.

